metadata.name: STOP WAR #1
metadata.description:
2/24/2022 5:00 AM:
Putin has officially declared war on sovereign independent Ukraine, which chose to go its own way in 2014.

3/2/2022:
6 days of brutal warfare across the country, destroying the people of Ukraine and civilians.

8 years of hybrid warfare that has already taken the lives of several thousand people.

Stop the war, stop Putin, before it is too late...

#stopputin #ukraine #stopwar #standwithukraine
